# cfv

Calculate and verify file checksums recursively on directory tree

## Usage

Usage: `cfv [OPTIONS] DIR [DIR2 ...]`

### Options

`--algo b3|md5|sha256|sha512`		Select hash algorithms. Default: `b3`

`--check`				Check existing checksums instead of creating those (which is default)

`--update`				Check and update existing checksums

`--summary`				Create a summary file with all the checksums in addition to the per directory checksum files. 
